'''Tayana''' was a meteor crater on [[Duro/Legends|Duro]]. It contained ancient ruins of a former surface city which reached its height in [[220 BBY/Legends|220 BBY]], before the [[Duros/Legends|Duros]] built their space cities. [[Gateway]] was built within Tayana. It itself was located in the [[Tayana district]].

